Rule 2378 (Power=1.5)
The Justiciar

      The Justiciar is an office; its holder is responsible for hot
      and cold running justice.

      Initial Posture is an Agora Nomic switch, tracked by the
      Justiciar in eir monthly report, with the same values and
      default value as Posture.  The Justiciar CAN flip Initial
      Posture by announcement.  The default value of Posture is the
      current value of Initial Posture.

      If the Justiciar's Posture is neither Standing nor Sitting, then
      it is flipped to Sitting.
